      "rationale": "Bench test conditions documented with calibrated flow meters (±1% accuracy), tachometers (±0.5%), and temperature-controlled blood analog (bovine blood, 37 ± 0.5°C). Five operating points span the clinically relevant CPB range (2–6 L/min, 3000–5000 RPM). Boundary conditions applied in CFD match measured test inlet/outlet conditions within measurement uncertainty.",
