      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry as used in the COU. Operating conditions (flow rates, rotational speeds, fluid properties) match the CPB clinical envelope. Blood analog (bovine blood) is the ASTM F1841-recommended fluid for hemolysis testing. Geometric fidelity confirmed by CMM measurement of test article versus CAD nominal.",
